{
  "info": {
    "name": "School Management API",
    "description": "Professional API Collection for School Management System",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "health"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Verifies that the API server is running and responsive.\n\n**Status Codes:**\n- 200: Server is healthy and running\n\n**Use Case:** Monitoring, load balancer health checks, continuous integration"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Add School",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Pre-request script to validate coordinates are within valid ranges",
              "console.log('Adding new school...');"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Test script to validate response",
              "pm.test('School added successfully', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([201, 200]);",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.equal(true);",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.schoolId).to.be.a('number');",
              "    ",
              "    // Save the school ID for later use",
              "    pm.environment.set('lastSchoolId', jsonData.schoolId);",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Delhi Public School\",\n  \"address\": \"123 Education Lane, New Delhi, India\",\n  \"latitude\": 28.5355,\n  \"longitude\": 77.2030\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/addSchool",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "addSchool"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Adds a new school to the database.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- name (string, required): School name (2-100 characters)\n- address (string, required): Complete address (5-200 characters)\n- latitude (number, required): Geographic latitude (-90 to 90)\n- longitude (number, required): Geographic longitude (-180 to 180)\n\n**Response (201 Created):**\n- success (boolean): Whether the operation was successful\n- message (string): Confirmation message\n- schoolId (number): ID of newly created school\n\n**Error Response (400 Bad Request):**\n- Occurs when validation fails\n- Returns array of validation errors\n\n**Use Case:** Registering new schools in the system"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "List Schools (All)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Schools retrieved successfully', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.equal(true);",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.schools).to.be.an('array');",
              "    ",
              "    // Verify distance calculation",
              "    if (jsonData.schools.length > 0) {",
              "        jsonData.schools.forEach(function(school) {",
              "            pm.expect(school.distance).to.be.a('number');",
              "            pm.expect(school.distance).to.be.at.least(0);",
              "        });",
              "    }",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/listSchools?latitude=40.7128&longitude=-74.0060",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "listSchools"
          ],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "latitude",
              "value": "40.7128",
              "description": "User's latitude (New York example)"
            },
            {
              "key": "longitude",
              "value": "-74.0060",
              "description": "User's longitude (New York example)"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Retrieves all schools sorted by proximity to the user's location.\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- latitude (number, required): User's latitude coordinate (-90 to 90)\n- longitude (number, required): User's longitude coordinate (-180 to 180)\n\n**Response (200 OK):**\n- success (boolean): Whether operation was successful\n- message (string): Response message\n- userLocation (object): Echo of user's coordinates\n- totalSchools (number): Total number of schools\n- schools (array): Array of schools with distance information\n  - Each school includes: id, name, address, latitude, longitude, distance (in km)\n\n**Distance Information:**\n- Calculated using Haversine formula\n- Represents great-circle distance on Earth\n- Returns distance in kilometers\n- Schools sorted by distance (nearest first)\n\n**Error Response (400 Bad Request):**\n- Invalid latitude or longitude\n- Out-of-range coordinates\n\n**Use Case:** Find schools near user, sorting by proximity, location-based queries"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "List Schools (Mumbai Location)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Response status is 200', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
              "});",
              "",
              "pm.test('Schools are sorted by distance', function () {",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    var schools = jsonData.schools;",
              "    ",
              "    for (let i = 1; i < schools.length; i++) {",
              "        pm.expect(schools[i].distance).to.be.at.least(schools[i-1].distance);",
              "    }",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/listSchools?latitude=19.0760&longitude=72.8777",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "listSchools"
          ],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "latitude",
              "value": "19.0760",
              "description": "Mumbai latitude"
            },
            {
              "key": "longitude",
              "value": "72.8777",
              "description": "Mumbai longitude"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Example: Retrieve schools sorted by proximity to Mumbai, India coordinates."
      },
      "response": []
    },
